emporary period of dumbness for his lack of faith (Luke 1), and of a more obscure figure, Zacharias son of Barachias, who was slain ‘between the temple and the altar’ (Matthew 23:35; Luke 11:51). In the United States it is familiar as the name of a 19th-century president,  Zachary Taylor . Since the 1990s the name has been remarkably popular in the English-speaking world, especially in the United States."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Y Bach ap Gwaethfoed of Gwent was born about 1170, in Wales as the son of Gwaethfoed ap Dryw. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"about 1170–":"umbes 1170–Surnud","1165–Male":"1165–Surnud","1170–Male":"1170–Surnud","1194–1234":"1194–1234","1135–Male":"1135–Surnud","about 1170":"umbes 1170","1135":"1135","1234":"1234","1165":"1165","1194":"1194","1170":"1170","Wales":"Wales"},"fi":{"about 1170–":"noin 1170–Kuollut","1165–Male":"1165–Kuollut","1170–Male":"1170–Kuollut","1194–1234":"1194–1234","1135–Male":"1135–Kuollut","about 1170":"noin 1170","1135":"1135","1234":"1234","1165":"1165","1194":"1194","1170":"1170","Wales":"Wales"},"fr":{"about 1170–":"environ 1170–Décédé","1165–Male":"1165–Décédé","1170–Male":"1170–Décédé","1194–1234":"1194–1234","1135–Male":"1135–Décédé","about 1170":"environ 1170","1135":"1135","1234":"1234","1165":"1165","1194":"1194","1170":"1170","Wales":"Galles","lifeSummary":"Y Bach ap Gwaethfoed of Gwent est né environ 1170, à Galles, fils de Gwaethfoed ap Dryw. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"about 1170–":"um 1170–Verstorben","1165–Male":"1165–Verstorben","1170–Male":"1170–Verstorben","1194–1234":"1194–1234","1135–Male":"1135–Verstorben","about 1170":"um 1170","1135":"1135","1234":"1234","1165":"1165","1194":"1194","1170":"1170","Wales":"Wales","lifeSummary":"Y Bach ap Gwaethfoed of Gwent wurde um 1170 in Wales, als Sohn von Gwaethfoed ap Dryw geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 1170–":"about 1170–Desede","1165–Male":"1165–Desede","1170–Male":"1170–Desede","1194–1234":"1194–1234","1135–Male":"1135–Desede","abo